Muhammad Iqbal Gujjar Son of CH Sultan Ahmed (born on July 6, 1943 in India) is a prominent national politician, parliamentarian and Chairperson in a Privilege Community in the 2013 Sharif-led cabinet from Pakistan Muslim League (N). A key Member of Parliament in Pakistan and a lawyer by profession. Chaudhry Muhammad Iqbal is married and has seven children.
